   Okabe–Ito color system
   ============================ */
$oi-blue:        #0072B2;  /* headings / structure */
$oi-green:       #009E73;  /* links */
$oi-black:       #000000;
$oi-grey:        #999999;
$oi-orange:      #E69F00;  /* for warnings/notes */
$oi-yellow:      #F0E442;  /* for highlights */

Colors and Hex Codes
Black: #000000
Orange: #E69F00
Sky Blue: #56B4E9
Bluish Green: #009E73
Yellow: #F0E442
Blue: #0072B2
Vermilion: #D55E00
Reddish Purple: #CC79A7
Grey: #999999 (or sometimes black is replaced with grey in 8-color sets) 

